transcript:
Customer: Hello?
Customer: Hello, hello.
Executive: Ji boliye sir.
Customer: Good morning. Kumar baat kar raha hai India Mart head office se sir. Bataiye.
Customer: Maine sir call kiya hai services feedback ke liye kiya hai. Abhi jo services aapki chal rahi hai uske bare mein.
Customer: Kab call aa raha hai sir abhi?
Customer: Yaar main traffic mein hu. Abhi office mein nahi hu.
Executive: Ha. To main kis time connect karu sir aapko?
Customer: Hello.
Executive: Ha kis time? Ab wo jo usme jo service portal pe wo Nikhil sir ka number hoga us pe baat kar lijiye. Wo wo dekhte hai India Mart ka kaam.
Customer: Thik hai sir, thik hai.
Executive: Okay.
summary:
Concerns:

- Executive called for service feedback.

- Customer is currently in traffic.



Resolution:

- Executive asked for a suitable time to call.

- Customer asked to contact Nikhil Sir.



Next Steps: 

None

Alert (If Any):

None
